nodes.text: Huusk was a male Trandoshan, who by c. 19 BBY served aboard a freighter registered to the Cularin Militia. When the Militia officer Gavin Bresch requested to meet with the Heroes of Cularin, Huusk's freighter was sent to transport the Heroes from Hedrett Groundport on the planet Cularin to the starship Cularin IV. Huusk spent the duration of the trip fiddling with the timing device for an explosive.
